H3.text: who is the guy that jumped from space. Felix Baumgartner

A4.text: Felix Baumgartner was widely known for jumping to Earth from a lickelium balloon in the stratosphere on 14 October 2012 as part of the Red Bull Stratos project.

A5.text: Joseph Kittinger's jump on 16 August 1960 set a record for free fall time, which Baumgartner's 2012 jump reduced by 17 seconds.

A6.text: Space Dive, BBC documentary about Baumgartner, 2012, 60 minutes

A7.text: Felix Baumgartner's jump from the stratosphere reached an altitude of 127,851 feet on 14 October 2012
